{"tid":699652,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"pgde 及教師前景一問，請讀過或者做緊老師既人入一入黎。","createTime":"2018-06-12T16:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T05:18:54.000Z","uid":69664,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e293d3d0d546d779a12e71c32f7f32ee6e3778b1","tid":699652,"uid":69664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"今年fresh grad 打算先做一年小學TA 睇下鍾唔鍾意教育，然後黎緊下一年報pgde，但係重有好多地方唔清楚希望有心人解答。（我非三大畢業，IELTS 8 分， 藝術方面都幾好，有芭蕾舞教師牌，同去教小學。）<br />\n<br />\n1. 有TA 位，係咪就好易去教大讀part time pgde programme  ? <br />\n<br />\n2. 浸大既pgde係咪認受性好低？<br />\n<br />\n3.pgde係咪會睇埋咩hon畢業？我係second low<br />\n<br />\n4. 係咪而家香港既教育市場都好差，未入行既就唔好入行？"},{"pid":"cace7ab6e127182b0de25b2f0d6d6a35acd9462f","tid":699652,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"邊科？"},{"pid":"c351daa8fecc1e3d3c30a4e1cdefe43f24e22438","tid":699652,"uid":69664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cace7ab6e127182b0de25b2f0d6d6a35acd9462f","tid":699652,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"邊科？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:47:03.000Z","msg":"英文"},{"pid":"34ff3c98382d549ee2b278f47420e486f4585e8f","tid":699652,"uid":129474,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:07:06.000Z","msg":"識人好過識字...<br />\n<br />\n而家個市況，小學出年會步入寒冬期(因2013年689停雙非，佢唯一嘅德政)，小一過埋今年龍年效應之後好多小學校長已經部署緊2019年9月點樣cut人...如果你想搵教席，除非你學歷好好，或識校長校監，否則都幾難搵到perm。合約的話，預左一年貨仔。<br />\n<br />\n反而中學就仲有6年好景，你不妨考慮下"},{"pid":"ac554b20eaf09d1675fdc96176825a736273442c","tid":699652,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:09:10.000Z","msg":"pgde只係張紙，邊間u都冇所謂，最緊要係本科成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd58e9ad9187240c0752253145b4c305fd0f35f3","tid":699652,"uid":69664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac554b20eaf09d1675fdc96176825a736273442c","tid":699652,"uid":52942,"like":1